room_title: Escape room "Annie's Footsteps" by ArtHatch Escape in San Marcos (CA)
room_description: For several years, strange occurrences have been happening in these woods. In fact just yesterday another local resident, Annie Anderson, went missing! As part of the community’s Search and Rescue efforts, your team has been tasked with investigating the mysterious cabin which belonged to Annie, to see what you might be able to learn. Be careful though! What you discover about this case may be more than your mind can handle…
